345
00:24:10,660 --> 00:24:11,690
Hal-hal

346
00:24:13,690 --> 00:24:14,830
seperti bercukur.

347
00:24:30,910 --> 00:24:32,009
Sakit.

348
00:24:36,309 --> 00:24:38,080
Terlepas dari semua itu,

349
00:24:38,820 --> 00:24:40,789
kamu tumbuh dengan baik.

350
00:25:13,219 --> 00:25:14,320
Sekarang...

351
00:25:18,660 --> 00:25:19,930
Hatiku terasa

352
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:21,860
tidak keruan lagi.

353
00:25:26,529 --> 00:25:30,170
Anda memikirkan cinta pertama Anda?

354
00:25:34,969 --> 00:25:36,039
Ya.

355
00:25:38,910 --> 00:25:42,080
Andai saja dia robot sepertimu.

356
00:25:54,690 --> 00:25:56,999
Aku pasti bisa mengelus rambutnya.

357
00:26:08,239 --> 00:26:09,509
Menggenggam tangannya.

358
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:16,479
Pergi ke berbagai tempat yang didatangi banyak orang.

359
00:26:22,850 --> 00:26:23,959
Serta,

360
00:26:40,870 --> 00:26:42,610
menciumnya.

361
00:26:47,249 --> 00:26:48,249
Itu keinginanku.

